\v 5 Themba eN\nd kosi\nd*ni ngenhliziyo yakho yonke\x + Hlab. 37.3,5. Hlab. 25.2.\x*, ungeyami ekuqedisiseni kwakho\x + Jer. 9.23.\x*.
