\v 7 Ungabi ngohlakaniphileyo emehlweni akho\x + 12.15. Roma 12.16.\x*; yesabe iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Jobe 1.1.\x*, usuke ebubini\x + Jobe 1.1.\x*\x + Jobe 28.28.\x*.
\v 8 Kuzakuba yikwelatshwa kwenkaba yakho, lokunathwayo kwamathambo akho\x + Jobe 21.24.\x*.
\v 9 Hlonipha iN\nd kosi\nd* ngemfuyo yakho, langezithelo zakho zokuqala zesivuno sakho sonke\x + Eks. 22.29. Mal. 3.10. Luka 14.13. Eks. 23.19.\x*.
