\v 11 Ndodana yami, ungadeleli ukulaya kweN\nd kosi\nd*, unganengwa yikukhuza kwayo\x + Jobe 5.17. Hlab. 94.12. Jak. 1.12. Isam. 3.19. Heb. 12.5,6.\x*.
\v 12 Ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* iyamlaya emthandayo, yebo, njengoyise indodana athokoza \add ngayo\x + Dute. 8.5. 1 Kor. 11.32.\x*\add*.
