\v 16 Ubude bezinsuku busesandleni sakho sokunene\x + 3.2.\x*, kwesokhohlo sakho inotho lodumo\x + 8.18.\x*.
\v 17 Izindlela zakho zizindlela zentokozo, lemikhondo yakho yonke iyikuthula\x + Mat. 11.29,30.\x*.
\v 18 Kuyisihlahla sempilo\x + 11.30. 13.12. 15.4. Gen. 2.9. 3.22. Isam. 2.7. 22.2.\x* kwabakubambayo, lobambelela kukho ubusisiwe\x + 4.13.\x*.
